import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';

import './Navigation.css'

function Navigation(){
    return(
        <Container fluid>
            <Navbar expand="lg">
                <Container>
                    <Navbar.Brand href="#home" className = "nav_link">React-Bootstrap</Navbar.Brand>
                    
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                    <Navbar.Collapse className="d-flex justify-content-end" id="basic-navbar-nav">

                    <Nav>
                        <Nav.Link href="#home" className='nav_link'>Home</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href="#link" className='nav_link'>Feature</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link href="#link" className='nav_link'>Style Guide</Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
        </Container>
    )
}

export default Navigation
